'''Rachuk roseola''' was an irritating skin inflammation, which was caused by a [[virus]] that was found in the [[Rachuk system/Legends|Rachuk system]], specifically on the [[Planet/Legends|world]] of [[Vladet]]. This form of roseola infected nearly every visitor to the planet, unless they were properly vaccinated prior to their arrival. When visiting the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] military base commanded by [[Admiral/Legends|Admiral]] [[Devlia]] on Vladet's [[Grand Isle]], [[Kirtan Loor]] contracted the virus.

